aakash is a 2005 indian kannada language action - drama film directed by mahesh babu , written by janardhan maharshi and produced by parvathamma rajkumar . the film stars puneeth rajkumar and ramya in the lead roles , while ashish vidyarthi and avinash play pivotal roles . the movie got mixed reviews from critics but was declared as a super hit at the box office . the film found a 175 days run at the cinema halls in karnataka . at the karnataka state film awards , the film won the best editor award for s. manohar .